.TH "nvme_init_set_features_rrl" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_rrl" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_rrl \- Initialize passthru command for Read Recovery Level
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_rrl
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "__u16 nvmsetid "  ","
.BI "__u8 rrl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "nvmsetid" 12
NVM set id
.IP "rrl" 12
Read recovery level setting
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_RRL
